a panic attack on air.

00:00:43.670 --> 00:00:48.442
And this was kind of an
inflection point for him.

00:00:48.442 --> 00:00:50.400
And he essentially did
what all of us would do,

00:00:50.400 --> 00:00:54.410
which is kind of investigate
the sources of his panic attack

00:00:54.410 --> 00:00:57.310
and what were the causes of it.

00:00:57.310 --> 00:01:02.300
And he used his journalism
platform as leverage

00:01:02.300 --> 00:01:07.040
