locking down meditation

00:52:35.660 --> 00:52:37.340
as a long-term habit.

00:52:37.340 --> 00:52:42.300
I know you mentioned
earlier in the talk

00:52:42.300 --> 00:52:44.590
once you start
realizing successes

00:52:44.590 --> 00:52:46.050
from a habit, that's
